MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Added floating math particles (π, ∑, √, ∫, ∞, etc.) for immersive atmosphere
- Implemented animated gradient orbs with organic floating motion
- Enhanced hero section with glowing CTA button and pulse animation
- Added scroll-triggered reveal animations with staggered delays
- Improved glassmorphism cards with hover lift and shine effects
- Created interactive course cards with unique color themes per HSC level
- Added icon hover animations (lift, rotate effects)
- Implemented gradient border waitlist card with success animation
- Enhanced navbar with scroll-aware glassmorphism effect
- Added new CSS animations: sparkle, success-pop, orb-float
- Extended Tailwind config with surface color variables
